---
title: Seed-Crusted Chicken Breasts with Roasted Beets
description: Who knew pumpkin and sunflower seeds make for the perfect crisp crust! A dazzling side of roasted beets, carrots and mashed potatoes get topped with crumbled goat cheese for layers of texture and flavour.
